--REGEXPECT--
01. Create subs with missing notification type, see error
=========================================================
HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
Content-Length: 86
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

{
    "description": "http, httpCustom, mqtt or mqttCustom is missing",
    "error": "BadRequest"
}


